## Benign findings — do NOT alert on these

These findings are informational and resolve on their own. Don't waste cycles investigating.

| Finding | Context | Benign when |
|---|---|---|
| `db_wallet_divergence wallet 24/0 vs DB 24/24` | Within first 90s of bot start | Transient — Sage wallet finished syncing within 2 more cycles |
| `dexie_visibility_gap` | Within 30s of offer creation | Dexie indexer catch-up delay |
| `coin_headroom_low` (severity=info) | Spare count > 0, just below target | Topup will fire within `COIN_PREP_COOLDOWN_SECS` |
| `orderbook_age_secs < 60` | During Dexie rate limit cooldown | Non-critical if < 120s |
| Offer count = `MAX_ACTIVE_BUY + active snipers` on a side | `SNIPER_ENABLED=True` and `sniper.active_snipes > 0` | Sniper offers live alongside the ladder. Ladder is the 24; sniper adds 1-2 per side. Compute expected total as `MAX_ACTIVE_{side} + sniper.active_{side}` before flagging drift. |

